            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div><p><a title="Companies > Capcom [2,662 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/capcom">Capcom</a> has released the teaser trailer for <em>Street Fighter </em>6 downloadable content character Ingrid, who is due out in late spring. <span id="more-1031000"></span></p><p><em><a title="Games > Street Fighter 6 [55 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/street-fighter-6">Street Fighter 6</a></em> is available now for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [11,514 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [8,796 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch 2 [1,049 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch-2">Switch 2</a>, <a title="Platforms > PS4 [28,737 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PlayStation 4</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [25,613 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1364780/Street_Fighter_6/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>.</p><p>Watch the trailer below.</p><h2><span>DLC Character Ingrid Teaser Trailer</span></h2><p><strong>English</strong></p><p><iframe title="Street Fighter 6 - Ingrid Teaser Trailer" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ysuw_40tnv4?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><!-- AD: content -->
